938
00:41:39,580 --> 00:41:41,100
Dashun, wait a moment.

939
00:41:41,900 --> 00:41:42,860
Shaohua, go ahead.

940
00:41:44,420 --> 00:41:45,300
What are you waiting for?

941
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:54,580
Shaohua.

942
00:41:59,740 --> 00:42:00,980
Try the soup I made.

943
00:42:04,700 --> 00:42:05,500
You made it?

944
00:42:06,100 --> 00:42:07,700
I followed your recipe.

945
00:42:07,900 --> 00:42:09,460
Not sure if it tastes the way it should.

946
00:42:09,780 --> 00:42:10,420
Sit down.

947
00:42:18,940 --> 00:42:20,300
It's good that you and your wife

948
00:42:21,340 --> 00:42:22,300
get along.

949
00:42:22,460 --> 00:42:24,500
But remember, everything needs balance.

950
00:42:26,140 --> 00:42:27,220
Overdo it, and it turns sour,

951
00:42:28,260 --> 00:42:28,860
you understand?

952
00:42:31,140 --> 00:42:31,700
Yes.

953
00:42:33,660 --> 00:42:34,900
Shaohua is capable.

954
00:42:36,580 --> 00:42:37,660
That's exactly

955
00:42:38,420 --> 00:42:40,220
why I chose her back then.

956
00:42:40,860 --> 00:42:42,340
But a capable woman

957
00:42:43,260 --> 00:42:44,220
often has a strong personality.

958
00:42:46,220 --> 00:42:47,300
Loving your wife

959
00:42:48,700 --> 00:42:50,460
is your role.

960
00:42:52,300 --> 00:42:53,660
But controlling her

961
00:42:55,620 --> 00:42:56,820
is your skill.

